PLEASE REPORT BBS PIRATES:
Apogee pursues ALL violators of our software copyrights.  If you post retail
copies of our software on your board you are in great danger of being fined
up to $50,000 in damages to our sales.  Our customers call us every day
reporting violators, so it is very hard not to be caught.  Remember, only
episode one of our game sets is distributed as shareware, and is clearly
marked.  The follow-up episodes may only be bought from Apogee or our many
authorized distributors.  As a member of the SPA, we have a great deal of
resources in prosecuting violators.

SPA Anti-piracy HOTLINE: 1-800-388-7478  Please call this line if you see any
BBS violating Apogee's copyrights, by making available Apogee's non-shareware
games.  Thank you for your support!

