                      Available in 256-color VGA only

             *** REQUIRES an 80286 or better system to run. ***

        *** AN ALL-NEW MISSION WITH 20 NEW LEVELS AND MUCH MORE! ***

This is a special commercial edition of the Wolfenstein 3-D saga, once again
starring the Allies' most durable agent, B.J. Blazkowicz.  In the midst of
the Nazi Blitzkrieg, the Spear that pierced the side of Christ is taken from
the Versailles and secured in the impregnable Castle Nuremberg.  According to
legend, no man can be defeated when he has the Spear.  Hitler believes himself
to be invincible with the power of the Spear as his army of destruction sweeps
across Europe.  (Historian's Note:  This mission actually takes place before
the original Wolfenstein 3-D game.)

Your mission is to recapture the Spear from an already unbalanced Hitler, with
the hope that the loss of his most coveted weapon will push him over the edge!
You must infiltrate the heavily guarded Nazi stronghold and time is running
out!

This is a full-sized epic game, not just an episode.  It has more than 20 huge
levels, four new fantastic boss enemies, new music and digitized stereo
sounds, new graphics, an incredibly scary ending, and much more.

There is not a shareware version of this game available, but you can be sure
that if you liked the original Wolfenstein 3-D six episodes, you'll like
this newer action-packed game even more.  Only $35!  Note:  The commercial
version, which is the exact same game Apogee offers, sells for $59--you save
$24 by ordering directly from Apogee.  Just call 1-800-GAME123 or use the
ORDER.FRM file to mail in your order.

(Order the original six episodes, plus Spear of Distiny, all for $85.)


