of Word Rescue is $15, or you can order (and register) all three volumes for
just $30.  As an incentive to order all three volumes, you'll also get the
hints sheet, the cheat codes, and a new bonus game from Apogee.  Plus, you can
call the Word Rescue hints line for assistance.  To order, call 1-800-GAME123.

